Name: trigger

Synonyms: triggered, triggering, trigger

Type: glossary

Description:
To cause an action to happen. In particular, to cause an <on> or
<setProp> <handler> to <execute>.

Also, the <set> instruction sent to an <object(glossary)> that triggers
a <setProp> <handler>.

References: set (command), on (control structure),
setProp (control structure), execute (glossary), handler (glossary),
object (glossary)

Tags: objects

